*FvwmForm-WinList: Text "X"
*FvwmForm-WinList: Input GeomY 6 ""
*FvwmForm-WinList: Text "Y  --  Font"
*FvwmForm-WinList: Input WLFont 40 ""
*FvwmForm-WinList: Line right
*FvwmForm-WinList: Text "Colorset"
