Tim, when you change an icon or title in a button, the window
shape is not updated.  Try this (replace the icon names first):

  DestroyModuleConfig FvwmButtons*
  KillModule FvwmButtons
  *FvwmButtonsRows 1
  *FvwmButtonsPixmap none
  *FvwmButtons(Icon icon1.xpm, Title foo)
  FvwmButtons

and then

  SendToModule FvwmButtons Title +0+0 bar
  SendToModule FvwmButtons Icon +0+0 icon2.xpm

Bye

Dominik ^_^  ^_^

